OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779865531
OL,3,CMan dies trying to save family from
OL,4,Cthe sea
OL,6,FA man has died in Cornwall after
OL,7,Ftrying to save two family members who
OL,8,Fgot into difficulty in the water.
OL,10,FPolice were called by the ambulance
OL,11,Fservice to a beach near Padstow around
OL,12,F3:50pm on bank holiday Monday 25 May.
OL,14,FA man was "suffering cardiac arrest in
OL,15,Fthe sea" at Tregirls Beach after he
OL,16,Fattempted to save two family members,
OL,17,Fpolice said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
