OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779865531
OL,3,CMan dies trying to save family from
OL,4,Cthe sea
OL,6,FHis family was brought to safety by
OL,7,Fmembers of the public, but the man,
OL,8,Fwho is local and in his 60s, was
OL,9,Fpronounced dead at the scene. His next
OL,10,Fof kin have been made aware.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Devon and Cornwall
OL,13,FPolice said: "We were called by the
OL,14,FAmbulance Service at around 3.50pm on
OL,15,FMonday 25 May following a report of a
OL,16,Fman suffering a cardiac arrest in the
OL,17,Fsea at Tregirls Beach, Padstow.
OL,19,F"It was reported he had entered the
OL,20,Fsea to try and assist two family
OL,21,Fmembers who had got into difficulty.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779865531
OL,3,CMan dies trying to save family from
OL,4,Cthe sea
OL,6,F"The family members were then brought
OL,7,Fto safety by members of the public.
OL,9,F"Emergency services and the RNLI
OL,10,Fattended the scene but sadly, the
OL,11,Flocal man in his 60s was pronounced
OL,12,Fdeceased at the scene. His next of kin
OL,13,Fare aware.
OL,15,F"The death is not being treated as
OL,16,Fsuspicious and a file will be prepared
OL,17,Ffor HM Coroner."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
